<ServiceHero
  eyebrow="Error Codes · Samsung, LG, Whirlpool, Bosch, Speed Queen, Miele · LA Same-Day"
  title="Washer Error Codes Repair Los Angeles"
  subtitle={`Display flashes a code, washer stops mid-cycle, customer Googles it. We decode and fix all major brands. Same-day across LA, Orange, Ventura, San Bernardino, Riverside. $89 residential diagnostic. ${phone}`}
  heroImageTitle="Washer Error Codes Repair"
